comments: Hield (SAC) makes hand on ball contact when contesting Smart's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) and Morris (BOS) engage and disengage off-ball without affecting the other's ability to freely move.
[Observable in enhanced video] Cauley-Stein (SAC) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Tatum (BOS) extends his off-arm and briefly grasps Bogdanovic's (SAC) left arm, but releases without affecting his ability to defend.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Bogdanovic (SAC)  initiates contact to Tatum's (BOS) side and left arm, affecting his jump shot attempt.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Smart's (BOS) path and does not deliver the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Fox (SAC) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
LLS and RLS show Horford (BOS) grazes Fox's (SAC) left arm as he looks to pass, but does not affect his ability to do so.
Hield (SAC) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage off-ball without affecting the other's ability to freely move.
Bjelica (SAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Tatum (BOS) after the release of his shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) is already in Morris' (BOS) path as brief contact occurs during the defensive switch.
Hayward (BOS) makes marginal contact with Hield's (SAC) front that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Bjelica (SAC) lifts his pivot foot at the start of the dribble.
Morris (BOS) makes marginal contact with Bjelica's (SAC) front that does not affect his SQBR or ability to pass.
Smart (BOS) loses his balance and begins to lose the ball prior to  Hield (SAC) making marginal contact to his front.
Morris (BOS) and Fox (SAC) make incidental contact with each other as they each attempt to gain control of the loose ball and do not affect the other's ability to do so.

Horford (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and makes some contact as he turns, but it is marginal and does not affect Hield's ability to defend through the screen.
Hield (SAC) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage off-ball without affecting the other's ability to freely move.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) commits the take foul on Tatum (BOS).
Hield (SAC) is already in Hayward's (BOS) path when contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Tatum (BOS) briefly extends his arms forward towards Barnes' (SAC) body but removes them as he moves towards the lane.
Hayward (BOS) makes contact with his hand to Hield's (SAC) side after the start of his upward shooting motion.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact with his left forearm to Hayward's (BOS) front after his gather.
Rozier (BOS) legally contests Barnes' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
